7
00:01:13.407 --> 00:01:14.742
Greetings. Collective.

8
00:01:14.876 --> 00:01:17.311
[male collective 7]
<i>Status. Dr. Corliss.</i>

9
00:01:19.047 --> 00:01:21.181
-Doctor.
-[clears throat]

10
00:01:21.315 --> 00:01:22.684
Design is stable.

11
00:01:23.216 --> 00:01:25.485
We're able to contain
quantum data

12
00:01:25.620 --> 00:01:28.056
through di-entangling it
into superposition.

13
00:01:28.455 --> 00:01:32.192
Functional. but the prototype
still has issues.

14
00:01:32.326 --> 00:01:34.094
If we want to succeed
at each setting.

15
00:01:34.227 --> 00:01:35.630
we're going to need
major changes.

16
00:01:35.763 --> 00:01:36.931
[female collective 1]
<i>Dr. Corliss.</i>

17
00:01:37.065 --> 00:01:38.198
<i>we have a time commitment</i>

18
00:01:38.332 --> 00:01:40.467
<i>regarding field applications.</i>

19
00:01:40.602 --> 00:01:43.236
[male collective 6]
<i>The Dreamcatcher must be ready.</i>

20
00:01:43.671 --> 00:01:47.341
There's just no way to compress
and translate this level of data

21
00:01:47.474 --> 00:01:52.279
without quantum
computational capabilities
and warping gravitational mass.

22
00:01:52.914 --> 00:01:55.750
[male collective 2]
<i>Why is this an issue?</i>

23
00:01:55.883 --> 00:02:00.822
Collective. we need something
with highly powerful
energy isotope

24
00:02:00.955 --> 00:02:02.356
to accomplish what you ask.

25
00:02:02.489 --> 00:02:05.459
Something that goes
well beyond the requirements

26
00:02:05.593 --> 00:02:07.427
of highly functioning AI.

27
00:02:07.562 --> 00:02:09.063
[male collective 8]
<i>We know of a way.</i>

28
00:02:09.196 --> 00:02:13.001
<i>Brightmore. please apprise her</i>
<i>once we adjourn.</i>

29
00:02:13.133 --> 00:02:14.535
My pleasure. Collective.

30
00:02:14.669 --> 00:02:16.838
[male collective 6]
<i>Dr. Corliss. finish the project</i>

31
00:02:16.971 --> 00:02:19.607
<i>within the time frame</i>
<i>we agreed to.</i>

32
00:02:19.741 --> 00:02:22.910
<i>or consequences will apply.</i>

33
00:02:23.044 --> 00:02:24.912
-I just need--
-[male collective 6]
<i>You will be given</i>

34
00:02:25.046 --> 00:02:26.614
<i>the resources you require.</i>

35
00:02:27.180 --> 00:02:30.585
[female collective 4]
<i>Can you abide</i>
<i>by the original agreement?</i>

36
00:02:31.052 --> 00:02:32.352
Yes. Collective.

37
00:02:32.486 --> 00:02:34.055
[male collective 8]
<i>Meeting adjourned.</i>

38
00:02:34.589 --> 00:02:36.323
-[low-pitched whirring]
-[buzzes]

39
00:02:36.456 --> 00:02:38.693
[suspenseful music]

40
00:02:38.826 --> 00:02:39.994
[whistles softly]

41
00:02:40.460 --> 00:02:42.362
Consequences. doctor.

42
00:02:43.196 --> 00:02:44.699
Feel free to take in the view.

43
00:02:48.503 --> 00:02:50.370
-[thunder crackling]
-[siren blares in the distance]

44
00:02:50.505 --> 00:02:52.205
