<i>Citizens of Silencia.</i>

45
00:02:52.339 --> 00:02:54.742
-[helicopter blades whirring]
<i>-Special curfew is in effect</i>

46
00:02:54.876 --> 00:02:57.812
<i>-due to...</i>
[continues indistinctly]
-[rain splattering]

47
00:03:06.319 --> 00:03:07.522
ETA?

48
00:03:08.956 --> 00:03:09.857
Five minutes.

49
00:03:11.859 --> 00:03:13.895
