50
00:03:16.130 --> 00:03:18.398
[automated voice on PA]
<i>Citizens of Silencia.</i>

51
00:03:18.533 --> 00:03:20.868
<i>Special curfew is in effect...</i>

52
00:03:21.002 --> 00:03:23.738
[continues indistinctly]

53
00:03:25.205 --> 00:03:28.643
<i>...no fireweapon discharges</i>
<i>past 10:00 p.m.</i>

54
00:03:29.143 --> 00:03:32.446
<i>-Soliciting is</i>
<i>strictly prohibited.</i>
-[engine revving]

55
00:03:33.081 --> 00:03:35.482
